title: Rito what are we going to do about this?
body:
today's league games are going all fine and dandy, as a matter of fact ive won 9 of my last 10 games! THEN RITO STRIKES {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wgmK5G2Y2ZE "excuse the language in this one!"

replies.body: Looks like your client ran into some issues with its installation being corrupted or otherwise damaged. I'd suggest running another quick repair through the client options to make sure everything's good, but also make sure to test the repairs in a custom game before queueing back up.
